## Augusta: Stats Baseline: Max Analysis
**Level 90 Confirmed Stats (S0, no echoes, with Forte Attribute Bonuses):**
- HP: ~14,283 (base)
- ATK: ~457 (base character ATK, before weapon); confirmed base ATK (Lv.90) from WuWaCompanion: 675 (this is combined character + weapon base at Lv.90 with Thunderflare Dominion)
- DEF: ~1,512 (approx)
- Base CRIT Rate: 5%
- Base CRIT DMG: 150%
- Max Energy: 125
- Forte Attribute Bonuses at max nodes: +12% Electro DMG Bonus, +12% ATK%

**Recommended Endgame Stats (S0, per Prydwen and Game8):**
- ATK: 2,100+ (minimum; higher is better)
- CRIT Rate: 70–80% (to achieve consistent crits; lower threshold than most DPS due to Crown of Wills Electro DMG Bonus making extra CRIT DMG valuable at S2)
- CRIT DMG: ~220–250% (target; Crown of Valor adds up to +20% additional)
- Heavy Attack DMG Bonus: as high as possible from substats

**Signature Weapon – Thunderflare Dominion (R1, Lv.90):**
- Base ATK: 675
- Secondary Stat: CRIT Rate 12.2%
- Passive R1: ATK +12%. Casting Intro Skill or Resonance Skill increases Heavy Attack DMG by +20% for 15s. Obtaining Shield allows Heavy Attack DMG to ignore 7.2% of the target's DEF for 7s, stacking up to 5 times (triggered once every 0.5s). Maximum DEF ignore at 5 stacks: 36%.
- Passive R5: ATK +24%. Heavy Attack DMG +40% for 15s. DEF ignore 12% per shield gain, up to 5 stacks (60% total).

## Augusta: Ascension Materials
Full Ascension (Lv.1 → Lv.90):

- **Luminous Calendula** (~60 total): Local specialty of Septimont, found specifically in the Sanguis Plateaus area of Rinascita. Cannot be pre-farmed before Version 2.6 release. Can be obtained from the Interactive Map.
- **When Irises Bloom** (Weekly Boss drop): Dropped by Fleurdelys — the Version 2.6 Weekly Boss. Approximately 14–16 required for full ascension.
- **Blighted Crown of Puppet King** (Boss material): Specific boss drop from Septimont-region bosses.
- **LF / MF / HF / FF Tidal Residuum** (enemy drops): Standard Rinascita enemy drops; ascending tiers required at each ascension level.
- **Waveworn Residue** series (210, 226, 235, 239): Obtained from Forgery Challenges or purchasable in cities.
- **Shell Credits:** Approximately 170,000 for full ascension to Lv.90.

