## Augusta: Team Composition Guide

## Augusta Best Team: Augusta + Iuno + Shorekeeper
**Role assignment:** Augusta (Main DPS) | Iuno (Sub-DPS / Heavy Attack Buffer) | Shorekeeper (Healer / Crit Buffer)

**Why this team:** Iuno provides a total of up to 90% DMG Amplification to Augusta through her kit — 40% All DMG + 50% Heavy Attack DMG — the latter being amplification that only Augusta can fully leverage via her shield-stacking interaction (Iuno's Full Moon Domain boosts Heavy Attack DMG when shields are generated). Shorekeeper provides CRIT Rate, CRIT DMG, team healing, and Stellarealm for additional utility. This is Augusta's highest-performing team as of Version 2.6–3.0.

**Team Rotation — Augusta + Iuno + Shorekeeper:**
1. Start with **Shorekeeper** → build Resonance and Concerto Energy via her internal combos → Activate Stellarealm → Switch to Iuno when her Intro is available
2. **Iuno** enters via Intro → immediately use Resonance Skill to activate Lunar Cycle → jump to enter New Moon state
3. In New Moon state → cast Liberation to fill Sentience points → 3 Basic Attacks + 2 Enhanced Resonance Skills to consume Forte energy
4. After consuming Sentience and filling Concerto Energy → Heavy Attack to activate Full Moon Domain → Switch to **Augusta**
5. **Augusta** enters → immediately perform Prowess-enhanced Heavy Attack combo → cast Echo Skill for Electro DMG
6. Cast Resonance Skill and Sword of Eternal Oath (base Liberation) + Heavy Attacks to build Ascendancy → perform Undying Sunlight chain (Strike → Leap → Plunge)
7. After Plunge grants 1st Majesty stack, Iuno's Outro effect should have provided the 2nd Majesty stack via Battlesong → Hold Liberation → Enter Sworn Allegiance
8. During Sworn Allegiance (7s): Attack 9× with Sunborne → cast Everbright Protector
9. After Sworn Allegiance: Additional Heavy Attack combo (HA + Stage 2–4)
10. Switch to Shorekeeper via Intro → Detonate Stellarealm
11. Repeat rotation

## Augusta Alternative Team 1: Augusta + Phrolova + Shorekeeper
**Role assignment:** Augusta (Main DPS) | Phrolova (Off-field DPS / Heavy Attack Amplifier) | Shorekeeper (Healer / Crit Buffer)

**Why this team:** Phrolova's Outro Skill grants 15% All-Type DMG Amplification + 25% Heavy Attack DMG Amplification. Augusta can fully leverage both. Phrolova's Hecate off-field damage adds independent DPS during Augusta's rotation windows. Shorekeeper handles sustain and provides CRIT Rate/DMG buffs.

**Team Rotation — Augusta + Phrolova + Shorekeeper:**
1. Start with **Shorekeeper** → build gauges → activate Stellarealm → switch to Phrolova
2. **Phrolova** → build 6 Volatile Notes via Basic Attack and Resonance Skill combos → once 6 notes ready, cast Scarlet Coda (enter Resolving Chord state)
3. Cast her Liberation during Resolving Chord → Hecate is summoned for off-field DPS → Switch to **Augusta** when Outro available
4. **Augusta** enters → Prowess-enhanced HA combo → Echo Skill → Resonance Skill + Liberation + HAs → Ascendancy to 100
5. Cast Undying Sunlight chain → Plunge → Hold Liberation → Enter Sworn Allegiance
6. Time stops for 7 seconds → 9× Sunborne → Everbright Protector
7. Augusta Heavy Attack combo → Switch back to Shorekeeper

*Recommended Echo Sets: Augusta — Crown of Valor (3pc) + Void Thunder (2pc); Phrolova — Dream of the Lost (3pc) + Havoc Eclipse (2pc)*

## Augusta Alternative Team 2: Augusta + Mortefi + Shorekeeper
**Role assignment:** Augusta (Main DPS) | Mortefi (Sub-DPS / Heavy Attack Buffer) | Shorekeeper (Healer)

**Why this team:** Mortefi's Outro grants 38% Heavy Attack DMG Amplification to the incoming Resonator for 14 seconds — the highest single Heavy Attack DMG buff among accessible supports for Augusta before Iuno was introduced. He also provides Fusion coordinated attack damage and ATK buffs. The team is straightforward and very effective.

**Team Rotation:**
1. **Shorekeeper** → build gauges → Stellarealm → switch to **Mortefi** (via Intro)
2. **Mortefi** → internal skill rotation to build Concerto Energy → activate Echo Skill buff for coordinated attacks → Outro Skill to give Augusta 38% Heavy Attack DMG buff
3. **Augusta** enters with 15% DMG Amp (Mortefi's Outro) + 38% Heavy Attack DMG → Prowess-enhanced Heavy Attacks → Echo Skill → RS + Liberation combos → Undying Sunlight Plunge → Sworn Allegiance
4. After Liberation: Heavy Attack combo → Outro → Mortefi re-enters → Repeat

