## Augusta: DPS Benchmarks

## Augusta DPS Benchmarks: S0 to S6 Relative Performance
*All benchmarks at full Lv.90 build, Crown of Valor 3pc + Void Thunder 2pc, The False Sovereign 4-Cost, Thunderflare Dominion R1, optimal rotation. Team: Augusta + Iuno + Shorekeeper (or equivalent). Data sourced from Wutheringlab and community analysis.*

| Sequence | Relative Performance | Notes |
|----------|---------------------|-------|
| S0       | 100% (baseline)     | Fully functional. S0 + signature weapon is the recommended stopping point for most players. |
| S1       | ~116%               | +16% from Crown of Wills × 2 stacks (30% Electro DMG Bonus + 30% Crit DMG). Interruption immunity on Enhanced RS is a major QoL gain. |
| S2       | ~145–155%           | Most impactful single node. +40% Crit Rate from Crown of Wills x2 enables conversion to up to +100% Crit DMG when overcapped. Dramatically changes optimal echo stat setup. |
| S3       | ~175–185%           | +25% across all major skill multipliers — a flat and significant damage node. |
| S4       | ~185–195%           | Team-wide +20% ATK buff from Intro adds moderate DPS uplift across the whole team. |
| S5       | ~188–198%           | Minimal personal DPS gain — primarily survivability improvement. |
| S6       | ~152% of S0 (Wutheringlab: +52% total)| 4×Crown of Wills, Thunder Rage procs, and enhanced Crit overcap scaling. Optimal Crit DMG echo swap at S6. |

*Note: "Overall, S6 provides approximately a 52% damage increase for Augusta" — Wutheringlab (August 2025). Prydwen community grading: Augusta is T1 DPS as of Version 2.7–3.0 meta.*

**Teams used for benchmarks (per Game8 and Prydwen):**
- **Best-in-slot benchmark:** Augusta + Iuno + Shorekeeper
- **Alternative benchmark:** Augusta + Mortefi + Shorekeeper
- **Accessible F2P benchmark:** Augusta + Mortefi/Phrolova + Verina

